    "Subsequently, the cross-modal mutual comprehension approach is given in step 2.",
    "This part is to equip the LLM with fundamental visual comprehension capabilities and achieve visual-language alignment.",
    "Particularly, the visual and language tokens are merged as the multimodal input for the unfrozen LLM tuning to enhance the interaction between the diverse visual and linguistic contexts.",
    "Finally, to address the limitations of the existing RS models are specialist ones, unable to handle multi-source and multi-task in one structure.",
    "A unified instruction tuning for RS method is developed in step 3."
